'''羅敏申路77號'''（{{lang-en|'''Robinson 77'''}}），舊稱新加坡航空公司大廈（SIA Building）<ref>{{ctbuh|2501|SIA Building}}</ref>，是一棟位於[[新加坡|新加坡]][[市中心_(新加坡)|市中心]][[珊頓道|珊頓道]]的[[摩天大樓|摩天大樓]]。大樓住址為羅敏申路77號，與{{le|華聯城|DBS Building Tower One}}毗鄰。<ref>{{cite web | title = Asia Travel : Map of SIA Building (S) 068896 | publisher = StreetDirectory.com | url = http://www.streetdirectory.com/asia_travel/travel/travel_id_7969/travel_site_3012/ | accessdate = 2008-02-05 | archive-date = 2012-12-09 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20121209134856/http://www.streetdirectory.com/asia_travel/travel/travel_id_7969/travel_site_3012/ | dead-url = no }}</ref>目前[[新加坡航空|新加坡航空]]總部並非設立在羅敏申路77號，其總部則是在樟宜的航空大樓。<ref>"{{cite web | url = https://www.singaporeair.com/en_UK/imprint/ | title = Airline Ground Positions | publisher = [[Singapore_Airlines|Singapore Airlines]] | accessdate = 11 July 2009 | archive-date = 2019-01-21 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190121152401/https://www.singaporeair.com/en_UK/imprint/ | dead-url = no }}"SIA Airline House 25 Airline Road, S(819829)"</ref><ref>"World Airline Directory." ''{{le|國際航空 (雜誌)|Flight International|Flight International}}''. 3–9 April 1996. [http://www.flightglobal.com/pdfarchive/view/1996/1996%20-%200815.html?search=%22Singapore%20Airlines%22 79] {{Wayback|url=http://www.flightglobal.com/pdfarchive/view/1996/1996%20-%200815.html?search=%22Singapore%20Airlines%22 |date=20160306095118 }}. "Airline House, 25 Airline Road 1781, Singapore"</ref>大廈建築面積約{{convert|27400|m2}}，並設有180個停車位。<ref>{{cite web | title = Robinson 77 Office | publisher = robinson77.com | url = http://www.robinson77.com/ | accessdate = 2008-02-05 | archive-date = 2020-01-24 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200124180705/http://robinson77.com/ | dead-url = no }}</ref>

== 歷史 ==
羅敏申路77號由SAA Partnership建築事務所設計，主承包商為[[大林組|大林組]]，結構工程師為[[林同棪|林同棪]]工程顧問股份有限公司。大廈於1998年完工，其他參與開發的公司包括[[新加坡航空|新加坡航空]]、PCR工程私人有限公司、里德·漢特利比公司（Rider Hunt Levett & Bailey）、利比建筑工料测量师有限公司（Levett & Bailey Chart, and Quantity Surveyors Ltd）等。

[[File:CPF_Building.JPG|thumb]]（圖中）。]]
== 建築結構 ==
羅敏申路77號是新加坡最早以全玻璃外牆結構的高層建築物，當時作為[[新加坡航空|新加坡航空]]總部，大廈側邊有著新加坡航空公司的標誌，建築物屋頂還設計成類似飛機[[尾翼|尾翼]]的設計。

== 售出 ==
2006年，[[新加坡航空|新加坡航空]]將羅敏申路77號出售給TSO投資公司（TSO Investment），該公司為[[里昂證券|里昂證券]]亞太恆富資本（CLSA Capital Partners）的附屬管理房地產單位。大廈最後以3億4390萬[[新加坡元|新加坡元]]售出，平均每平方英尺售價1,165元。根據房地產公司指出，這筆交易符合非核心商業戰略。在當時，大廈公告地價為1億1880萬元。[[新加坡航空|新加坡航空]]隨後將出售所得的款項用於投資，並使公司及其子公司成長。<ref>{{cite web|title=SIA sells its Robinson Rd building for $344m |publisher=SGHousing.com |url=http://www.sghousing.com/2006/06/29/sia-sells-its-robinson-rd-building-for-344m/ |accessdate=2008-02-05 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080723205154/http://www.sghousing.com/2006/06/29/sia-sells-its-robinson-rd-building-for-344m/ |archivedate=July 23, 2008 }}</ref>

2011年，第一太平戴维斯投资管理公司（Savills Fund Management，又稱SEB Investment GmbH）宣布將出售該建築。<ref>{{cite news | author=Jonathan Peeris | title=77 Robinson Road back on market - again | url=http://business.asiaone.com/property/news/77-robinson-road-back-market-again | work=The Business Times | date=June 23, 2016 | accessdate=June 24, 2016 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161122074423/http://business.asiaone.com/property/news/77-robinson-road-back-market-again | archive-date=2016-11-22 | dead-url=yes }}</ref>然而到2015年，第一太平戴维斯投资管理公司再度宣稱將出售該建築，<ref>{{cite news |author=Kalpana Rashiwala |author2=Lynette Khoo |url=http://www.businesstimes.com.sg/real-estate/77-robinson-road-back-on-the-market |title=77 Robinson Road back on the market |work=Business Times Singapore |date=2 September 2015 |accessdate=12 January 2016 |archive-date=2016-04-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160426235256/http://www.businesstimes.com.sg/real-estate/77-robinson-road-back-on-the-market |dead-url=no }}</ref>但由於該公司正進行所有權和管理的更動，隨後取消了該出售計劃。目前羅敏申路77號所有者為第一太平戴维斯投资管理公司。<ref>{{cite news |author=Shiwen Yap |url=http://www.dealstreetasia.com/stories/savills-im-acquires-seb-asset-management-11361 |title=Savills IM acquires SEB Asset Management |work=Business Times Singapore |date=2 September 2015 |accessdate=12 January 2016 |archive-date=2019-10-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191004013149/https://www.dealstreetasia.com/stories/savills-im-acquires-seb-asset-management-11361/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

